description:
The Pirate is back after an injury took her out of last season altogether, she was 3-0 before the injury. She is fit and ready to capture the glory she once possessed here at US. She was the Season 2 Overall Champion, and expects to regain that title this season.
Bobbi Starr is a feisty, takes no shit kind of girl. What she lacks in experience she gains in determination. Her size and strength will carry her far, but when she gains experience. Lookout. Until then enjoy Bobbi getting fucked in the ass for the first time on video anywhere.
WELCOME TO SEASON 4 OF ULTIMATE SURRENDER!
title: The Pirate(0-0) The Killer(0-0)
